    # "My phone buzzes in my pocket."
    "Mi teléfono vibra en el bolsillo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:13
translate spanish jez5_450455fc:

    # "It's Detective Rodriguez. I wonder if she's found something out about my dad."
    "Es la detective Rodríguez. Me pregunto si habrá averiguado algo sobre mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:16
translate spanish jez5_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:18
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:19
translate spanish jez5_31f304d3:

    # det "Hey, [pcname]."
    det "Hola, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:20
translate spanish jez5_704218da:

    # pc "Did you find anything?"
    pc "¿Has descubierto algo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:22
translate spanish jez5_dd220c64:

    # det "What? Oh! About your dad?"
    det "¿Qué? ¡Ah! ¿Sobre tu padre?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:24
translate spanish jez5_e8fe8a8c:

    # det "Oh God, no I'm sorry. I wasn't calling about your dad, but I can understand why you'd think that."
    det "Dios mío, no, lo siento. No te llamaba por tu padre, pero entiendo por qué lo has pensado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:25
translate spanish jez5_1559f8f9:

    # det "With me being a detective and on your dad's case and all."
    det "Ya que soy detective y estoy con el caso de tu padre y todo eso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:26
translate spanish jez5_8c3ac124:

    # det "God, I'm a horrible detective aren't I?"
    det "Dios, soy una detective horrible, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:27
translate spanish jez5_a807c23e:

    # pc "No, I don't think so. What did you call for then?"
    pc "No, no lo creo. ¿Entonces por qué me has llamado?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:30
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:31
translate spanish jez5_0a63889f:

    # det "Well, I had kind of a rough day and I wanted to talk to somebody."
    det "Bueno, he tenido un día un poco duro y quería hablar con alguien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:33
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:34
translate spanish jez5_ea09e714:

    # det "And you were nice to me in the past, when we went out for drinks."
    det "Y tú fuiste muy amable conmigo en el pasado, cuando salimos a tomar algo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:36
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:37
translate spanish jez5_307d2b53:

    # det "And I don't really have anybody else to talk to."
    det "Y la verdad es que no tengo a nadie más con quien hablar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:39
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_4.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_4.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:40
translate spanish jez5_0f2cd5d3:

    # det "So I was wondering if you would want to just talk some?"
    det "Así que me preguntaba si te apetecería charlar un rato."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:46
translate spanish jez5_47059538:

    # det "You're right. This was a mistake, I'm sorry."
    det "Tienes razón. Ha sido un error, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:47
translate spanish jez5_ec16f7c0:

    # det "I won't bother you any more until I have information on your dad."
    det "No te molestaré más hasta que tenga información sobre tu padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:48
translate spanish jez5_07fc1b9f:

    # det "Bye, [pcname]."
    det "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:52
translate spanish jez5_5429a27f:

    # "She hangs up and I lie down to go to sleep."
    "Cuelga y yo me acuesto para dormir."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:53
translate spanish jez5_ceaf3431:

    # "I can hardly believe that she wants to call me and dump her problems on me. Don't I have enough of my own to deal with?"
    "Me cuesta creer que quiera llamarme para descargar sus problemas en mí. ¿No tengo ya suficientes con los míos?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:54
translate spanish jez5_0a396100:

    # "I mean, my dad is missing and it doesn't seem like she's doing much of anything to find him."
    "Es decir, mi padre está desaparecido y no parece que ella esté haciendo gran cosa para encontrarlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:55
translate spanish jez5_a9441b54:

    # "Maybe I was a little harsh with her, but she needs to do her damn job."
    "Quizá fui un poco dura con ella, pero tiene que hacer su maldito trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:56
translate spanish jez5_437235da:

    # "I fall asleep, still upset about the whole thing."
    "Me quedo dormida, todavía enfadada por todo el asunto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:62
translate spanish jez5_9f04dd80:

    # det "My Chief is yelling at me all the time because I haven't been able to track down this meth manufacturer."
    det "Mi jefe no para de gritarme porque no he sido capaz de localizar a ese fabricante de metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:63
translate spanish jez5_2edb985d:

    # det "It's like, I'm trying. There's only so much I can do."
    det "Es que lo estoy intentando. No puedo hacer mucho más."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:64
translate spanish jez5_d637e4b1:

    # det "I spend most of my day on stakeouts watching drug handoffs."
    det "Me paso la mayor parte del día haciendo vigilancias para ver entregas de droga."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:65
translate spanish jez5_b65d63fc:

    # det "Or interrogating people, trying to push them into telling me something."
    det "O interrogando a gente, intentando presionarlos para que me digan algo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:66
translate spanish jez5_e4fde77f:

    # det "But nobody's giving anything up and I'm running out of leads."
    det "Pero nadie suelta nada y se me están acabando las pistas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:67
translate spanish jez5_45b6d6aa:

    # det "There's only two detectives on this case. A big meth ring and just two of us."
    det "Solo hay dos detectives en este caso. Una gran red de metanfetamina y solo nosotros dos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:68
translate spanish jez5_77a9cef6:

    # det "I mean Skyhill is a small town, so I get it, but I need more help here."
    det "Quiero decir, Skyhill es un pueblo pequeño, así que lo entiendo, pero necesito más ayuda aquí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:69
translate spanish jez5_72d52a4d:

    # det "I wish we could call in the state police, or the FBI or something, but the Chief won't have it. Says we have to handle this ourselves."
    det "Ojalá pudiéramos llamar a la policía estatal, o al FBI o algo así, pero el jefe no lo permite. Dice que tenemos que encargarnos de esto nosotros mismos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:70
translate spanish jez5_d8b3de1e:

    # det "But there's only so much I can do. I have other cases too - like your dad's - that I'm having to neglect because of this meth thing."
    det "Pero hay un límite a lo que puedo hacer. También tengo otros casos —como el de tu padre— que estoy teniendo que descuidar por culpa de este asunto de la metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:72
translate spanish jez5_88d7e875:

    # det "And today I had to raid the house of this methhead."
    det "Y hoy he tenido que hacer una redada en la casa de una adicta a la metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:73
translate spanish jez5_d5874b9e:

    # det "It was horrible. This woman, her house was disgusting. Her baby, a three-year-old girl, was sitting in the middle of a bunch of filth naked."
    det "Ha sido horrible. Esa mujer, su casa era asquerosa. Su bebé, una niña de tres años, estaba sentada desnuda en medio de un montón de porquería."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:74
translate spanish jez5_2823a872:

    # det "And I had to take this child, who was screaming and crying that she didn't want to leave her mom, and give the child to protective services."
    det "Y tuve que llevarme a esa niña, que gritaba y lloraba porque no quería dejar a su madre, y entregarla a los servicios sociales."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:75
translate spanish jez5_e5dd6ea8:

    # det "The girl will probably have a better life in foster care than she would have with her mother, but who knows. She could end up with some abusive assholes or something."
    det "Probablemente la niña tendrá una vida mejor en acogida que la que tendría con su madre, pero quién sabe. Podría acabar con unos capullos maltratadores o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:76
translate spanish jez5_5e97fe72:

    # det "That little girl's life is messed up no matter what happens now."
    det "La vida de esa niña está jodida pase lo que pase ahora."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:77
translate spanish jez5_a1286de7:

    # det "And it just makes me so sad."
    det "Y eso me pone muy triste."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:78
translate spanish jez5_89052a8b:

    # pc "I'm sorry. That's awful."
    pc "Lo siento. Es horrible."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:80
translate spanish jez5_97380cd0:

    # det "So I get the woman back to the station and start interrogating her."
    det "Así que me llevo a la mujer a la comisaría y empiezo a interrogarla."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:81
translate spanish jez5_3e4784a1:

    # det "She's going to jail for at least five years for possession, probably will get a child endangerment charge as well, but she won't give up her dealer."
    det "Va a ir a la cárcel al menos cinco años por posesión, probablemente también le imputen un delito de poner en peligro a una menor, pero no delata a su camello."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:82
translate spanish jez5_19e09092:

    # det "I don't fucking get it."
    det "No lo cojo, joder."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:83
translate spanish jez5_59760784:

    # det "She's scared that something will happen to her family if she snitches."
    det "Tiene miedo de que le pase algo a su familia si chiva."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:84
translate spanish jez5_c0f63ffe:

    # det "Spits in my face, calls me a pig. I wanted to beat her fucking head in."
    det "Me escupe en la cara, me llama cerdo. Me dieron ganas de partirle la puta cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:85
translate spanish jez5_c36e96d1:

    # det "Then I get chewed out by the Chief because I didn't get anything out of her."
    det "Luego me echa la bronca el jefe porque no le saqué nada."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:87
translate spanish jez5_2288ac26:

    # det "And that was my day."
    det "Y así fue mi día."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:88
translate spanish jez5_2074c381:

    # det "I'm just so tired of all of it. I want to find this meth manufacturer and shut that shit down."
    det "Estoy tan cansado de todo esto. Quiero encontrar a ese fabricante de metanfetamina y acabar con esa mierda."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:90
translate spanish jez5_3a7bef84:

    # "I think about telling her about the bunker that Izzy had sent me to."
    "Pienso en contarle lo del búnker al que Izzy me había enviado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:91
translate spanish jez5_35c47a4d:

    # "But I'm not sure that is really what she's looking for."
    "Pero no estoy seguro de que eso sea realmente lo que ella busca."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:92
translate spanish jez5_7dda6c8a:

    # "Plus, I'm not sure if me and Izzy might get in some serious trouble for our part in whatever they were doing."
    "Además, no sé si Izzy y yo podríamos meternos en un buen lío por nuestra participación en lo que fuera que estuvieran haciendo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:93
translate spanish jez5_9fcbf4b8:

    # "I may tell Jez about it later, but for now I stay quiet."
    "Quizá se lo cuente a Jez más tarde, pero por ahora me callo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:95
translate spanish jez5_6387c117:

    # "I think about telling her about the bunker that Reba had taken me to."
    "Pienso en contarle lo del búnker al que Reba me había llevado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:96
translate spanish jez5_35c47a4d_1:

    # "But I'm not sure that is really what she's looking for."
    "Pero no estoy segura de que eso sea realmente lo que ella quiere oír."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:97
translate spanish jez5_306cf091:

    # "Plus, I'm not sure if Reba might get in some serious trouble for our part in whatever they were doing."
    "Además, no estoy segura de si Reba podría meterse en un buen lío por nuestra participación en lo que fuera que estuvieran haciendo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:98
translate spanish jez5_9fcbf4b8_1:

    # "I may tell Jez about it later, but for now I stay quiet."
    "Quizá se lo cuente a Jez más tarde, pero por ahora me callo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:99
translate spanish jez5_a3049ca4:

    # det "Anyway, thanks for listening to me vent."
    det "En fin, gracias por escucharme desahogarme."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:100
translate spanish jez5_732596c5:

    # det "I needed to get all that off my chest."
    det "Necesitaba sacarme todo eso de encima."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:101
translate spanish jez5_d957ecb7:

    # pc "You feeling better now?"
    pc "¿Te sientes mejor ahora?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:103
translate spanish jez5_880af095:

    # det "A little, yeah."
    det "Un poco, sí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:104
translate spanish jez5_566089d7:

    # det "You're a pretty good listener, [pcname]. Thank you."
    det "Eres muy buena escuchando, [pcname]. Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:105
translate spanish jez5_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "Cuando quieras."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:107
translate spanish jez5_1d1792a8:

    # det "I can be a good listener too, if you ever want to chat."
    det "Yo también sé escuchar bien, si alguna vez te apetece charlar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:108
translate spanish jez5_d87a672d:

    # det "You could call me at nights and we could just talk or something."
    det "Podrías llamarme por las noches y podríamos simplemente hablar o algo así."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:110
translate spanish jez5_b7c62ab4:

    # pc "That sounds good. I'll do that."
    pc "Suena bien. Lo haré."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:112
translate spanish jez5_fc19b673:

    # det "Good."
    det "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:114
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_5.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_5.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:115
translate spanish jez5_22567fb7:

    # det "Okay, [pcname], I better get to bed. Thanks for listening to me."
    det "Vale, [pcname], mejor me voy a la cama. Gracias por escucharme."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:117
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_6.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_6.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:118
translate spanish jez5_22b369a9:

    # det "I'll talk to you later."
    det "Hablamos luego."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:119
translate spanish jez5_31e08f47:

    # pc "Okay, good night, Jez."
    pc "Vale, buenas noches, Jez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:121
translate spanish jez5_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice 'voices/jez_night.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_night.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:122
translate spanish jez5_8669dcbe:

    # det "Night."
    det "Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:125
translate spanish jez5_52d6e3cf:

    # "We hang up and I get ready for bed."
    "Colgamos y me preparo para irme a la cama."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:126
translate spanish jez5_73bafe8e:

    # "It must be hard having to deal with the things that she deals with, see the things that she sees every day."
    "Debe de ser duro tener que lidiar con las cosas con las que ella lidia, ver las cosas que ve cada día."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:127
translate spanish jez5_63d39c7b:

    # "I like that she is opening up to me though, becoming more friendly."
    "Aunque me gusta que se esté abriendo conmigo, que se esté volviendo más amistosa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:128
translate spanish jez5_00f887ed:

    # "I actually really like her."
    "De hecho, me cae muy bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:129
translate spanish jez5_c6ddf2e1:

    # "I fall asleep thinking about how I'd like to spend more time with her. Hopefully we'll get a chance soon."
    "Me duermo pensando en cómo me gustaría pasar más tiempo con ella. Espero que tengamos la oportunidad pronto."

